        <h2
          class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4"
        >
          📚 推薦書籍
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          這一區收錄了對我影響深刻的書籍，並簡單分享我的閱讀收穫。
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- 書籍 1: Code Complete -->
        <div
          class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300 magic-card card-3d"
        >
          <div class="aspect-[3/4] bg-white">
            <img
              src="/testimonials1.png"
              alt="Code Complete：軟體建構實務指南"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">
              Code Complete：軟體建構實務指南
            </h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-3">
              作者：Steve McConnell
            </p>
            <p
              class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4 leading-relaxed"
            >
              程式設計經典，內容涵蓋軟體建構的原則、最佳實踐與大量範例，幫助初學者建立正確的程式設計觀念與寫出高品質程式碼。
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900 text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-200 text-xs rounded-full hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-200"
